H1_description: H1: Aggregates from many sources and forwards almost unchanged to few addresses. May indicate ransomware or scam fund routing.

H3_description: H3: Receives funds from a single source and distributes to many addresses. May indicate laundering or scam profit distribution.

H2_description: H2: Aggregates from many sources but shows no outgoing transfers. May indicate scam fund storage or ransomware holding address.
